<item>
            <title>[LU-9090] increase default RPC size to 4MB</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9090</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The default RPC size is still 1MB, even though it could be increased to 4MB. This should be accompanied by a change to the default stripe size to also be 4MB so that widely-striped files can generate full RPCs without pinning so much memory on the client. This should provide a noticeable improvement in performance for streaming read/write workloads.&lt;/p&gt;

